k\" href=\"/blog\"><span class=\"text-ink/30\" aria-hidden=\"true\">├──</span><svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" class=\"h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-ink/45 group-hover:text-ink/70\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2.6 5.4c0-.6.5-1 1-1h4l1.6 1.9h7.2c.6 0 1 .4 1 1v8.4c0 .6-.4 1-1 1H3.6c-.5 0-1-.4-1-1V5.4Z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg><span class=\"\">writing/</span></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-1.5 whitespace-nowrap font-mono text-sm transition-colors text-ink/70 hover:text-ink\" href=\"/contact\"><span class=\"text-ink/30\" aria-hidden=\"true\">└──</span><svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" class=\"h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-ink/45 group-hover:text-ink/70\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5.5 2.7c-.6 0-1 .4-1 1v12.6c0 .6.4 1 1 1h9c.6 0 1-.4 1-1V7.1L11.8 2.7H5.5Z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path><path d=\"M11.6 2.9v3.8c0 .5.4.9.9.9h3.6\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg><span class=\"\">contact.txt</span></a></nav><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-ring disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 border bg-background shadow-sm hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground h-9 w-9 border-ink/20 md:hidden\" aria-label=\"Open navigation\" type=\"button\" aria-haspopup=\"dialog\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"radix-:Rdkq:\" data-state=\"closed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu h-4 w-4\"><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"12\" y2=\"12\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"6\" y2=\"6\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"18\" y2=\"18\"></line></svg></button></div></header><div class=\"pt-14\"><main class=\"mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 pb-8 sm:px-6\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-6 py-10 text-center sm:flex-row sm:items-start sm:text-left\"><img src=\"/imgs/profile-pic.png\" alt=\"Abdihamid Moallim\" class=\"h-28 w-28 shrink-0 rounded-full border border-ink/15 object-cover sm:h-32 sm:w-32\"/><div class=\"min-w-0\"><h1 class=\"text-3xl sm:text-4xl\">Abdihamid Moallim</h1><p class=\"mt-1.5 text-ink/60\">Software engineer</p><p class=\"mt-4 max-w-xl text-base leading-relaxed text-ink/80\">I build web apps, internal tools, and AI-backed products: ERP systems, SaaS, client sites. Based in Mogadishu, working remote.</p><div class=\"mt-5 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3 sm:justify-start\"><a href=\"/imgs/resume.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-ring disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 shadow h-9 px-4 py-2 gap-2 bg-clay text-cream hover:bg-clay/90\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-file-down h-4 w-4\"><path d=\"M15 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7Z\"></path><path d=\"M14 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4\"></path><path d=\"M12 18v-6\"></path><path d=\"m9 15 3 3 3-3\"></path></svg>Resume</a><a href=\"/contact\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-ring disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 border bg-background shadow-sm hover:bg-accent h-9 px-4 py-2 gap-2 border-ink/20 text-ink hover:border-clay/50 hover:text-clay\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-mail h-4 w-4\"><rect width=\"20\" height=\"16\" x=\"2\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7\"></path></svg>Get in touch</a></div></div></div><section id=\"about\" class=\"scroll-mt-20 py-10 \"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 200 12\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" class=\"mb-8 h-3 w-full text-ink/15\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M1 6c8-4 14 4 22 1s13-6 21-2 15 6 22 2 14-6 21-1 15 5 22 1 13-6 21-2 15 6 22 2 14-5 21-1 13 5 22 0\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" fill=\"none\"></path></svg><div class=\"mb-5 flex flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-2\"><div><div class=\"font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-clay\">about.md</div><h2 class=\"mt-1\">About</h2></div></div><div class=\"grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-[1fr,1fr]\"><div class=\"space-y-4 text-ink/80\"><p>I&#x27;m a software engineer working across web apps, AI tooling, and internal systems, mostly for small businesses that need something built and shipped, not just prototyped.</p><p>I run Lama Tools, a small AI and automation consultancy, and lead ICT at Shakir Group. Before that: IT support, graphic design, and a couple of startups.</p><p>Also co-organized IndabaX Somalia 2023 and spoke at IRISE Hub and the Abdiaziz Youth Center on AI and freelancing.</p><p class=\"text-sm text-ink/50\">Unrelated to any of this: I&#x27;m slowly working toward a pilot&#x27;s license.</p></div><div><div class=\"mb-3 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-ink/40\">Work</div><ul class=\"space-y-3\"><li class=\"flex flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-x-3 border-b border-ink/10 pb-2.5\"><span><span class=\"font-medium text-ink\">Lama Tools</span><span class=\"text-ink/50\"> · <!-- -->Founder</span></span><span class=\"font-mono text-xs text-ink/40\">Dec 2024 – present</span></li><li class=\"flex flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-x-3 border-b border-ink/10 pb-2.5\"><span><span class=\"font-medium text-ink\">Shakir Group</span><span class=\"text-ink/50\"> · <!-- -->Head of ICT</span></span><span class=\"font-mono text-xs text-ink/40\">Oct 2023 – present</span></li><li class=\"flex flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-x-3 border-b border-ink/10 pb-2.5\"><span><span class=\"font-medium text-ink\">Byteso Tech</span><span class=\"text-ink/50\"> · <!-- -->Co-founder</span></span><span class=\"font-mono text-xs text-ink/40\">May 2022 – Aug 2023</span></li><li class=\"flex flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-x-3 border-b border-ink/10 pb-2.5\"><span><span class=\"font-medium text-ink\">Target Marketing</span><span class=\"text-ink/50\"> · <!-- -->IT Personnel</span></span><span class=\"font-mono text-xs text-ink/40\">Aug 2021 – Nov 2021</span></li><li class=\"flex flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-x-3 border-b border-ink/10 pb-2.5\"><span><span class=\"font-medium text-ink\">Print Sign</span><span class=\"text-ink/50\"> · <!-- -->Graphic Designer</span></span><span class=\"font-mono text-xs text-ink/40\">Nov 2020 – Apr 2021</span></li><li class=\"flex flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-x-3 border-b border-ink/10 pb-2.5\"><span><span class=\"font-medium text-ink\">SOCSOYU</span><span class=\"text-ink/50\"> · <!-- -->Volunteer IT Advisor</span></span><span class=\"font-mono text-xs text-ink/40\">Mar 2019 – Aug 2019</span></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"mt-8 border-t border-ink/10 pt-6\"><div class=\"mb-2.5 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-ink/40\">Tools</div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-1.5\"><span class=\"border border-ink/10 px-2 py-1 font-mono text-xs text-ink/60\">JavaScript</span><span class=\"border border-ink/10 px-2 py-1 font-mono text-xs text-ink/60\">TypeScript</span><span class=\"border border-ink/10 px-2 py-1 font-mono text-xs text-ink/60\">Next.js</span><span class=\"border border-ink/10 px-2 py-1 font-mono text-xs text-ink/60\">React</span><span class=\"border border-ink/10 px-2 py-1 font-mono text-xs text-ink/60\">Node.js</span><span class=\"border border-ink/10 px-2 py-1 font-mono text-xs text-ink/60\">Python</span><span class=\"border border-ink/10 px-2 py-1 font-mono text-xs text-ink/60\">PHP</span><span class=\"border border-ink/10 px-2 py-1 font-mono text-xs text-ink/60\">Flutter</span><span class=\"border border-ink/10 px-2 py-1 font-mono text-xs text-ink/60\">PostgreSQL</span><span class=\"border border-ink/10 px-2 py-1 font-mono text-xs text-ink/60\">MySQL</span><span class=\"border border-ink/10 px-2 py-1 font-mono text-xs text-ink/60\">MongoDB</span><span class=\"border border-ink/10 px-2 py-1 font-mono text-xs text-ink/60\">Supabase</span><span class=\"border border-ink/10 px-2 py-1 font-mono text-xs text-ink/60\">Prisma</span><span class=\"border border-ink/10 px-2 py-1 font-mono text-xs text-ink/60\">Tailwind CSS</span><span class=\"border border-ink/10 px-2 py-1 font-mono text-xs text-ink/60\">Git</span><span class=\"border border-ink/10 px-2 py-1 font-mono text-xs text-ink/60\">Cloudflare</span></div></div></section><section id=\"work\" class=\"scroll-mt-20 py-10 \"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 200 12\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" class=\"mb-8 h-3 w-full text-ink/15\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M1 6c8-4 14 4 22 1s13-6 21-2 15 6 22 2 14-6 21-1 15 5 22 1 13-6 21-2 15 6 22 2 14-5 21-1 13 5 22 0\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" fill=\"none\"></path></svg><div class=\"mb-5 flex flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-2\"><div><div class=\"font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-clay\">projects/</div><h2 class=\"mt-1\">Selected work</h2></div><div class=\"font-mono text-xs text-ink/40\"><a class=\"hover:text-clay\" href=\"/projects\">view all →</a></div></div><div class=\"grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"border border-ink/12 p-4\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-2\"><h3 class=\"text-base\">Decisionfy</h3><span class=\"shrink-0 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-ink/40\">Live</span></div><p class=\"mt-1.5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink/65\">AI data analyst for e-commerce sellers. Upload a CSV or Excel export from Shopify or WooCommerce and ask it questions directly instead of building a dashboard yourself.</p><div class=\"mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-1.5\"><span class=\"border border-ink/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-[10px] text-ink/50\">Next.js</span><span class=\"border border-ink/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-[10px] text-ink/50\">Supabase</span><span class=\"border border-ink/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-[10px] text-ink/50\">E2B</span><span class=\"border border-ink/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-[10px] text-ink/50\">Claude API</span></div></div><div class=\"border border-ink/12 p-4\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-2\"><h3 class=\"text-base\">Shakir Portal</h3><span class=\"shrink-0 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-ink/40\">Private</span></div><p class=\"mt-1.5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink/65\">Internal HR and payroll system for Shakir Group: employee records, payroll runs, and approvals in one place.</p><div class=\"mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-1.5\"><span class=\"border border-ink/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-[10px] text-ink/50\">Next.js</span><span class=\"border border-ink/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-[10px] text-ink/50\">Prisma</span><span class=\"border border-ink/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-[10px] text-ink/50\">MongoDB</span></div></div><div class=\"border border-ink/12 p-4\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-2\"><h3 class=\"text-base\">Amin Energy &amp; Cargo ERP</h3><span class=\"shrink-0 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-ink/40\">Private</span></div><p class=\"mt-1.5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink/65\">A 16-module ERP with a client portal, covering operations end to end for an energy and cargo business. Built under LamaTools.</p><div class=\"mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-1.5\"><span class=\"border border-ink/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-[10px] text-ink/50\">Next.js</span><span class=\"border border-ink/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-[10px] text-ink/50\">Supabase</span></div></div><div class=\"border border-ink/12 p-4\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-2\"><h3 class=\"text-base\">Shakir Group web platforms</h3><span class=\"shrink-0 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-ink/40\">Live</span></div><p class=\"mt-1.5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink/65\">Four sites for Shakir Group’s corporate presence and business units, including a vehicle fitment lookup I built for Shakir General covering years and models across the Somali market.</p><div class=\"mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-1.5\"><span class=\"border border-ink/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-[10px] text-ink/50\">Next.js 15</span><span class=\"border border-ink/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-[10px] text-ink/50\">Cloudflare</span></div></div></div><a class=\"mt-5 inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-mono text-sm text-clay hover:underline\" href=\"/projects\">See all projects<svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 14\" class=\"h-3 w-6\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M1 7c6-1.5 12-1 22 .3\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path><path d=\"M17 1.5c2.5 2 4.5 3.8 6 5.6-1.7 1.2-4 3-6 5.4\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" fill=\"none\"></path></svg></a></section></main><footer class=\"border-t border-ink/10 py-6\"><div class=\"mx-auto flex max-w-6xl flex-col items-center justify-between gap-3 px-4 text-sm text-ink/50 sm:flex-row sm:px-6\"><p>© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> Abdihamid Moallim</p><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/abmoallim/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"transition-colors hover:text-clay\">L